## ğŸ“ Basic usage

```python
from topolib.elements.node import Node
from topolib.topology.topology import Topology

n1 = Node(1, 'A', 10.0, 20.0)
n2 = Node(2, 'B', 11.0, 21.0)
topo = Topology(nodes=[n1, n2])
# Add links, compute metrics, visualize, etc.
```

